snippet.title: Consequences Showcase | Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader
snippet.description:
Every action has consequences, especially if you are a daring explorer of the void of the Koronus Expanse. Want to take a peak on how the galaxy will react to you? Then, check out our new video which is just about that!

Join the Beta: https://roguetrader.owlcat.games/

Add the game to your wishlist:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2186680/Warhammer_40000_Rogue_Trader/
